				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Astarion bit Karlach No Touch in gameplay. Astarion got BURNED, a short dialog between Karlach and Astarion. Several possible lines:\r\n1. Party doesn't know that Astarion is a vampire. Astarion is shocked he can't bite Karlach, Karlach is shocked Astarion is a vampire.\r\n2. Party knows Astarion is a vampire. Karlach tells him she is too hot for him."
